snippet.title: Official Ms. Splosion Man iOS Launch Trailer
snippet.description: Ms. Splosion Man for iOS is finally here.  Enjoy the official trailer.  Go check out the game on the App Store for the low price of $2.99!!  https://itunes.apple.com/us/app/ms.-splosion-man/id589642458?mt=8
